<div id="post-335" class="cf post-335 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-uncategorized">

	<h2>
		<span class="post-format"></span>
		<a href="http://werblog.com/2002/11/another-observation-from-the/" title="Another observation from the" rel="bookmark">Another observation from the</a>
		
	</h2>

	
	
	<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
	
		<div class="post-date">		
			<p class="post-month">Nov</p>
			<p class="post-day">6</p>
			<p class="post-year">2002</p>				
		</div>

		Another observation from the conference &#8212; the media industry is still obsessed with Tivo. All of the entertainment company CEOs have brought it up, whether as a threat, an opportunity, or something they can successfully compete against. Tivo CEO Mike Ramsay is speaking tomorrow. All this attention doesn&#8217;t guarantee that Tivo the company will survive and thrive, but it reinforces my belief that they are onto something deep and important.
		
	</div>

